From c6ff3a0efc40a48c51fe88b734b84c0319abf6a4 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sat, 13 Jun 2026 05:40:24 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add live data-driven Overview dashboard with compliance score
 engine

Adds GET /api/dashboard/overview which aggregates consent_events, widget_configs
and integrations via count-only queries to compute a real-time DPDP compliance
score, total consents collected, acceptance rate (today/7d/30d), active purpose
count, and pending rights requests. Renders these via new ComplianceScoreCard
and StatCard components on the portal Overview page, replacing the old static
stats row.
